pullRequest.title: Be consistent about optimized Parquet writer being experimental
pullRequest.bodyText:
The optimized Parquet writer is still experimental and was described as
in session property's description. This makes the naming and
descriptions consistent.
Relates to: #5518

nodes.bodyText: If we do not care about backward compatiblity regarding session property maybe we can drop @LegacyConfig from config property too?
